# frontier-execute

Use this skill when executing an approved campaign task in `{{ project_name }}`.

## Workflow

1. Read `AGENTS.md`, `frontier.yaml`, and the active campaign artifacts.
2. Confirm the task boundary and affected files.
3. Make the smallest useful change.
4. Run relevant validation.
5. Update progress or handoff notes.

Do not merge, deploy, or cross repository boundaries without explicit human approval.
